folder: Middagh Street & Willow Street, Brooklyn, NY
text:
24 Middagh Street, at the S.E. corner of Willow Street. This place was used as a Chop-house in 1815. Still standing in (1929).

1922.

Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.

folder: Middagh Street & Willow Street, Brooklyn, NY
text:
24-32 Middagh Street, south side, between Willow and Hicks Streets. The corner house was a chop house in 1815. It became a residence in 1836.

April 1925.

Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
